Now you don't even knock.

19
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,320
I'm sorry, Mr. Lin.

20
00:01:35,839 --> 00:01:37,119
I just got the news.

21
00:01:37,279 --> 00:01:39,440
Mr. Jiang and Mr. Lei
are going to hold a press conference

22
00:01:39,559 --> 00:01:40,759
in order to
respond to the acquisition.

23
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,119
It's been a while since Hengshan Fund has

24
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,279
announced to acquire Yutian.

25
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,559
How will Yutian respond to that?

26
00:01:50,639 --> 00:01:52,440
What actions will Yutian take?

27
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,600
Will Yutian accept
the acquisition or not?

28
00:01:55,399 --> 00:01:57,279
Thank you for your concern for Yutian.

29
00:01:58,039 --> 00:02:00,440
About how Yutian will
deal with the acquisition,

30
00:02:00,759 --> 00:02:02,800
my assistant Lei Yuzheng

31
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:03,839
will tell you more details.

32
00:02:04,479 --> 00:02:06,240
Why is Lin Xiangyuan not here?

33
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:07,720
As far as we know,

34
00:02:07,839 --> 00:02:09,240
Lin Xiangyuan, the CEO of Yutian,

35
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,360
supports the acquisition.

36
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,240
Can he represent the board?

37
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,679
(Friends from the media,)

38
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,000
(I think you all want to know)

39
00:02:17,399 --> 00:02:19,240
(the attitude of Yutian
toward this acquisition.)

40
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,399
Mr. Lin,

41
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,600
why didn't you go to
the press conference?

42
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,000
If I went there, what shall I say?

43
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,759
Right.

44
00:02:31,399 --> 00:02:32,839
You could not say
you support the acquisition.

45
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,880
You could not say
you're against the acquisition either.

46
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,399
It's good for you to be absent.

47
00:02:41,679 --> 00:02:42,600
(In simple words,)

48
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,520
(the attitude of the board is...)

49
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,679
The attitude of the Board of Yutian

50
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:56,000
is to accept the acquisition.

51
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,919
What? Accept?

52
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,320
(But)

53
00:03:00,399 --> 00:03:02,039
(we only accept the acquisition)

54
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,279
(that is good to
Yutian's future development.)

55
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,479
(If the acquirer
wants to use the acquisition)

56
00:03:06,559 --> 00:03:07,960
(to cover their malice,)

57
00:03:08,679 --> 00:03:11,479
Yutian will take legal action.

58
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,360
Lei Yuzheng

59
00:03:18,679 --> 00:03:20,160
acknowledged failure.

60
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,880
But look at him.

61
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,559
In such a cocky way,

62
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,720
he is still pretending.

63
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:25,800
Stop annoying me. Will you get out?

64
00:03:28,399 --> 00:03:30,119
(Yutian is a good listed company.)

65
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,279
(Since Yutian was listed,)

66
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,360
(the achievements of Yutian)

67
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,880
(have been seen by all of you.)

68
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:36,960
(Someone wants to acquire Yutian today.)

69
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:38,080
(What does it mean?)

70
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,520
(I advise you to think about it.)

71
00:03:40,279 --> 00:03:41,600
(It means Yutian has great value.)

72
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,600
(Right.)

73
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,160
(This exactly means
Yutian has great value)

74
00:03:44,239 --> 00:03:45,440
(and good development in future.)

75
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,799
Who

76
00:03:47,359 --> 00:03:48,519
will acquire

77
00:03:48,519 --> 00:03:50,040
a company which is weak.

78
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,440
(So,)

79
00:03:52,559 --> 00:03:54,559
(this is the reason
of Yutian being acquired.)

80
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,600
Thank you for your concern for Yutian.

81
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:01,799
Acquisition?

82
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,119
Why is it being acquired?

83
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,359
Go. Let's ask.

84
00:04:05,799 --> 00:04:07,920
Mr. Jiang, do you mean that
Yutian will accept the acquisition?

85
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,320
Mr. Jiang and Mr. Lei, please reply.

86
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,920
Acquisition will take quite a long time.

87
00:04:12,279 --> 00:04:13,519
No one can know the result yet.

88
00:04:14,239 --> 00:04:15,720
Yutian will not be thrown to the wolves.

89
00:04:16,239 --> 00:04:17,200
You will see!

90
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,640
Mr. Lei. Mr. Lei...

91
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,640
Can you please tell more, Mr. Lei?

92
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,320
Tell us more...

93
00:04:26,888 --> 00:04:28,936
(Mr. Yu)

94
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:38,440
Mr. Lin, what does Lei Yuzheng mean?

95
00:04:38,679 --> 00:04:40,399
We're in the same boat.

96
00:04:40,679 --> 00:04:42,480
You can't get away from it either.

97
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,239
We have invested
more than a billion yuan.

98
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,480
We will not give up.

99
00:04:48,359 --> 00:04:50,079
You can't act as nothing happened.

100
00:04:50,359 --> 00:04:51,480
About what you should do,

101
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:53,239
I think we don't need
to remind you, right?

102
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,480
Besides, your town fellow,

103
00:04:55,679 --> 00:04:57,440
is controlled by us.

104
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,679
About the consequence,

105
00:04:58,799 --> 00:04:59,959
you should think twice!

106
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:03,720
Don't talk to me like that.

107
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,320
Cooperate or not, and how to cooperate,

108
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,320
that's up to me.

109
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,000
You don't need to tell me.

110
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,480
Mr. Lin, you have to think it over.

111
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,040
This is all because of you.

112
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,359
Is this what I wanted it to be?

113
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,119
I've done my best.

114
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,480
What else do you want me to do?!

115
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,640
Now,

116
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,600
you insist to do the acquisition.

117
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,359
You guys are really greedy!

118
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:29,959
Let me tell you.

119
00:05:30,559 --> 00:05:32,880
Now it is you beg me, not I beg you.

120
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,239
What do you mean?

121
00:05:35,679 --> 00:05:37,600
Do you want to get rid of all of it?

122
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,880
We are not the same kind of person.

123
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,279
I will be more than happy
to break off with you.

124
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:43,239
Remember that you are
the one who is begging me.

125
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,480
In the future, I hope

126
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,760
you do not teach me what to do.

127
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,839
Buddy,

128
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,480
I watched the press conference.

129
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:04,559
Well done!

130
00:06:05,679 --> 00:06:07,959
What you said is awesome!

131
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:11,519
After your mom passed away, your dad

132
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:14,480
had been feeling sorry to you.

133
00:06:15,359 --> 00:06:17,559
He had always been thinking about
how to make up for you.

134
00:06:18,559 --> 00:06:21,399
That's why he set up
this trust fund for you.

135
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,320
When I was little, I thought it was fun

136
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,040
and once stole it from my dad's office.

137
00:06:26,239 --> 00:06:27,279
Why was it kept by you?

138
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:30,320
It was kept by Zhenrong's dad.

139
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,640
After he passed away, it was kept by me.

140
00:06:33,239 --> 00:06:34,359
But what's this?

141
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,559
This is the proof of your identity.

142
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:42,600
By the way, for this trip,

143
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,920
don't tell anyone.

144
00:06:44,359 --> 00:06:46,480
Don't worry. I know what to do.

145
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,880
Uncle Lin, I am Yuzheng.

146
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,119
Yuzheng.

147
00:07:05,679 --> 00:07:06,920
I haven't seen you for many years.

148
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,959
Same as you were little!

149
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:13,040
After all these years, you've grown up

150
00:07:13,799 --> 00:07:14,760
and I'm getting old.

151
00:07:15,359 --> 00:07:16,679
Let's go inside.

152
00:07:16,799 --> 00:07:17,559
OK.

153
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,640
This is what your father gave to me.

154
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,359
Now it's time to return it to its owner.

155
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,720
Uncle Lin, please have a check.

156
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:49,032
(Trust Fund Plan.
Consignor: Yutian Group)

157
00:08:10,679 --> 00:08:11,520
I remember that

158
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,679
your dad is a few years
younger than I am.

159
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,760
But he passed away ahead of me.

160
00:08:17,479 --> 00:08:19,520
Uncle Lin, that was because of me.

161
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,520
It's OK. I know

162
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,719
it was not all your fault.

163
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:27,400
Things keep changing, so does life.

164
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,919
After a few years,
I think I can't work anymore.

165
00:08:31,559 --> 00:08:33,280
The hope will be placed on you.

166
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,440
Don't say that, Uncle Lin.

167
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,840
You look really well.

168
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,799
But the inside is the cotton waste.

169
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:40,840
I'm getting older and older.

170
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,039
In all my life,

171
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,880
there are not many people I respect.

172
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,239
Your dad was one of them.

173
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,799
Yuzheng,

174
00:08:51,119 --> 00:08:52,640
you are now in charge of Yutian.

175
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:55,400
I can't teach you how to manage it.

176
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,159
But I have to tell you.

177
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,640
You should learn from your dad.

178
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:02,280
A man who does great things
should be tolerant of others.

179
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,799
One thing that I respect most of him is

180
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,359
that your dad was tolerant,

181
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,400
even of the opponents.

182
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,599
It is really hard to do that.

183
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,840
I watched the news of China.

184
00:09:14,239 --> 00:09:15,080
I know that Yutian

185
00:09:15,119 --> 00:09:17,280
is facing a big crisis.

186
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:20,679
I hope you can overcome it very soon.

187
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,239
Thank you, Uncle Lin.

188
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:26,280
Mr. Lin, the documents are OK.

189
00:09:26,599 --> 00:09:27,479
OK.

190
00:09:28,479 --> 00:09:30,280
All these documents are checked.

191
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,200
Now, this trust fund

192
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,640
can be deployed at your disposal.

193
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,799
What do you want to do with it?

194
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:39,400
Do you want to use it to save Yutian?

195
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,880
To be honest,
I haven't made the decision.

196
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:47,599
Think before you do. That's correct.

197
00:09:49,239 --> 00:09:51,599
I believe that you will
spend the money wisely.

198
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,840
After making a decision,

199
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,400
I will email you.

200
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,840
Would you want me to show you around
in Malaysia for a few days?

201
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:58,479
That's very kind of you.

202
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,400
But I have to go back today.

203
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,640
Such a hurry.

204
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:02,719
Yes.

205
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:04,679
You know, it is so urgent.

206
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:08,359
I can understand.
It's quite a hard time.

207
00:10:09,359 --> 00:10:10,719
Then I won't keep you.

208
00:10:11,359 --> 00:10:12,640
Wish you all the best!

209
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,359
I will wait for your good news here.

210
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,039
Two glasses of water, please.

211
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,200
Yuzheng,

212
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,119
you are so melodramatic.

213
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,200
Please enjoy it, sir.

214
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:39,559
Thank you.

215
00:10:39,719 --> 00:10:41,200
Having dinner in a suit.

216
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:44,719
