220
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,080
Only one T-shirt.

221
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,520
Please have a look at the menu, sir.

222
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,440
Take a bite of his meal,

223
00:10:56,719 --> 00:10:57,840
and then go to work.

224
00:10:58,479 --> 00:10:59,799
But you,

225
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,799
even for a dinner,
you have to make it quite formal.

226
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:02,880
I think

227
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,400
you are already used to
the clothes in the jail,

228
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,599
the yellow one?

229
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:09,559
Do you know why you are still single?

230
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,719
You are too boring.

231
00:11:14,239 --> 00:11:15,599
Too boring?

232
00:11:16,479 --> 00:11:18,520
I just don't want to
waste time and money

233
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:21,960
on such kind of trivia,
like eating and getting dressed.

234
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,039
Waste?

235
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,599
In my world,

236
00:11:24,719 --> 00:11:26,119
I have no idea on "waste".

237
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:29,840
To me, all kinds of
waste are reasonable.

238
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:31,679
OK. OK. OK.

239
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,400
I give up.

240
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:34,679
Siyang.

241
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,840
I keep thinking about one thing.

242
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,919
Do you still remember that Vodafone

243
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:42,799
acquired their

244
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,559
third largest telecom provider

245
00:11:44,599 --> 00:11:46,000
Orange?

246
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:49,599
It was the one that owned
by Li Jiacheng.

247
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:50,760
Orange Telecom?

248
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:52,559
Yes, exactly.

249
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:53,520
I remember.

250
00:11:54,119 --> 00:11:55,919
I was studying abroad at that time.

251
00:11:56,359 --> 00:11:57,559
For this acquisition,

252
00:11:57,799 --> 00:11:59,520
the two foreign companies

253
00:11:59,719 --> 00:12:01,520
took a long time for the dispute.

254
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:03,239
The famous company Vodafone

255
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,799
wanted to acquire the telecom company.

256
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,559
But

257
00:12:06,719 --> 00:12:08,599
it was acquired by Germany's Mannesmann.

258
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,359
Vodafone was infuriated

259
00:12:11,479 --> 00:12:13,640
and acquired Mannesmann.

260
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,080
Do you think

261
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:18,919
who was the winner?

262
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,159
That should

263
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:22,960
be Li Jiacheng.

264
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:24,679
After the acquisition,

265
00:12:25,359 --> 00:12:26,919
he could earn a billion euros more.

266
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,159
That was a lot!

267
00:12:31,239 --> 00:12:32,200
Yuzheng,

268
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,159
are you planning to turn Yutian

269
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:36,119
into "Orange"?

270
00:12:39,919 --> 00:12:40,760
We'll see.

271
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,679
Order, please.

272
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,919
I forgot my purse.

273
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,280
