302
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,239
So much fun.

303
00:14:36,719 --> 00:14:38,679
I haven't seen
such interesting show for a long time.

304
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,440
And I didn't expect that
I am also involved.

305
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:42,320
Yuzheng,

306
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,599
S.G is the backer of Hengshan.

307
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:47,239
You have done such a thing.

308
00:14:47,679 --> 00:14:50,000
S.G should definitely know it's you.

309
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:53,880
In this way, Linton

310
00:14:55,039 --> 00:14:56,119
can't stand it anymore.

311
00:14:59,176 --> 00:15:00,328
(Jiang Jin)

312
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,440
It is so late. Who are you calling?

313
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:08,880
Uncle Jiang.

314
00:15:10,159 --> 00:15:11,200
Yuzheng.

315
00:15:11,679 --> 00:15:13,440
