317
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,039
Would you please

318
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,960
tell our company's security agent that

319
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:20,840
if Yutian's stock
drops sharply tomorrow,

320
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,000
they shall

321
