322
00:15:25,559 --> 00:15:26,640
Why?

323
00:15:27,039 --> 00:15:28,159
I can't tell you now.

324
00:15:28,559 --> 00:15:29,640
Please wait for two more days.

325
00:15:30,119 --> 00:15:31,400
