337
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:02,640
Isn't it about to be acquired?

338
00:16:04,119 --> 00:16:05,119
Acquisition?

339
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,479
Yutian is a large company.

340
00:16:07,599 --> 00:16:09,000
