348
00:16:42,839 --> 00:16:43,800
No.

349
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:45,760
Really?

350
00:16:46,439 --> 00:16:47,280
Mr. Lin,

351
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:48,839
