353
00:16:50,599 --> 00:16:51,640
OK, I believe you.

354
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:52,920
Go.

355
00:17:03,040 --> 00:17:04,400
Mr. Lei has meetings in the afternoon.

356
00:17:04,479 --> 00:17:06,119
