371
00:17:39,439 --> 00:17:40,880
How about we sit down there and talk?

372
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:42,760
You're flying to Beijing tomorrow?

373
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,040
I'm afraid I will not be available.

374
00:17:44,479 --> 00:17:45,920
Why don't we just talk over the phone?

375
00:17:46,599 --> 00:17:47,719
Then I'll be straight forward.

376
00:17:47,839 --> 00:17:50,599
There is an oversea
company acquiring S.G.

377
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,280
I believe

378
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:53,719
