382
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:02,000
For my sake,

383
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:03,439
give S.G a chance.

384
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,880
You are beginning to speak
more and more like a Chinese.

385
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:09,920
But I'm sorry. There is no turning back.

386
00:18:10,199 --> 00:18:11,319
S.G,

387
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,280
I will definitely get it!

388
00:18:24,104 --> 00:18:25,608
(Mr. Yu)

389
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,719
The stock of Yutian has dropped sharply.

390
00:18:32,319 --> 00:18:33,319
Tell me

391
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:35,000
what's going on?

392
00:18:35,560 --> 00:18:37,479
The stock market is risky.

393
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:39,280
It's normal that the stock price drops.

394
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,319
You should be very experienced.

395
00:18:42,359 --> 00:18:43,839
You should know more than I do.

396
00:18:43,959 --> 00:18:44,839
Mr. Lin,

397
00:18:45,079 --> 00:18:47,560
if you sell all your shares of Yutian

398
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,599
and cooperate with me

399
00:18:48,719 --> 00:18:50,680
to make sure the
acquisition is successful...

400
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:51,880
I guarantee you that

401
00:18:52,319 --> 00:18:54,199
if you don't give up Hengshan
as soon as possible,

402
00:18:54,479 --> 00:18:56,040
you will lose more.

403
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:58,439
It could be ten times more.

404
00:18:58,560 --> 00:18:59,520
Yuzheng,

405
00:19:00,319 --> 00:19:01,719
I chose Hengshan,

406
00:19:02,119 --> 00:19:03,959
just to make Yutian better.

407
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,479
I think

408
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:07,880
you know Hengshan better than I do.

409
00:19:08,439 --> 00:19:10,479
Hengshan always does
things by unfair means.

410
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,000
Among the companies
acquired by Hengshan,

411
00:19:12,119 --> 00:19:14,119
