412
00:19:14,239 --> 00:19:15,319
Besides,

413
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,439
I invited you in,

414
00:19:17,800 --> 00:19:19,199
expecting for a rescue,

415
00:19:19,319 --> 00:19:20,520
not destruction.

416
00:19:20,719 --> 00:19:21,800
Unfortunately,

417
00:19:21,959 --> 00:19:22,920
Linton.

