422
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:30,680
Mr. Lin,

423
00:19:30,839 --> 00:19:32,680
my last advice.

424
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:34,959
If you don't want to
lose everything you've got,

425
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:37,359
