Sincerity?

427
00:19:38,599 --> 00:19:40,920
You don't have to threaten me
again and again.

428
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:43,319
You are abusing my sincerity.

429
00:19:43,439 --> 00:19:44,400
What do you mean?

430
00:19:44,479 --> 00:19:45,400
You are now telling me that

431
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:47,439
you want to share weal

432
00:19:47,439 --> 00:19:48,520
and woe with Yutian.

433
00:19:48,599 --> 00:19:49,560
Yes.

434
00:19:49,959 --> 00:19:51,680
Do you think you can?

435
00:19:52,439 --> 00:19:54,439
I gave you money. I gave you dignity.

436
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:55,800
I gave you everything.

437
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,920
Now you're trying to betray me.

438
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,079
Without me,

439
00:19:59,199 --> 00:20:00,640
even for another ten years,

440
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:02,319
you will still be nobody.

441
00:20:02,479 --> 00:20:04,040
I can be on this position,

442
00:20:04,439 --> 00:20:05,839
not because you helped me.

443
00:20:05,959 --> 00:20:07,599
It's Lei Yuzheng who helped me.

444
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:10,439
Linton,

445
00:20:11,359 --> 00:20:13,280
I'm now answering your call.

446
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:15,400
