have good relationship.

447
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:17,920
Yuzheng,

448
00:20:18,239 --> 00:20:20,520
if we break the contract now,
we will lose a lot of money.

449
00:20:21,319 --> 00:20:22,880
After tomorrow,

450
00:20:23,959 --> 00:20:24,959
I can't guarantee

451
00:20:25,079 --> 00:20:26,319
