452
00:20:37,479 --> 00:20:38,319
Xie Li.

453
00:20:40,839 --> 00:20:41,839
This is Lin Xiangyuan.

454
00:20:42,119 --> 00:20:43,079
Where is Xie Li?

455
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,040
Where is he?

456
00:20:47,479 --> 00:20:48,439
