run my studio well.

509
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,560
If he is happy,

510
00:23:02,599 --> 00:23:04,199
I can do anything.

511
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:08,920
There are many ways to leave someone.

512
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:14,040
But for me, I will choose
to leave quietly

513
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:16,160
